1
00:00:06,016 --> 00:00:09,920
(2005, a week before An Ruoxi's murder)

2
00:00:13,364 --> 00:00:14,124
Ruoxi,

3
00:00:14,323 --> 00:00:15,563
didn't expect you.

4
00:00:16,323 --> 00:00:17,056
Let me tell you.

5
00:00:17,056 --> 00:00:17,312
You...

6
00:00:22,684 --> 00:00:24,164
What's wrong?

7
00:00:24,484 --> 00:00:25,763
Is someone following you?

8
00:00:26,283 --> 00:00:27,883
I checked when I came in.

9
00:00:28,283 --> 00:00:29,004
It's nothing.

10
00:00:29,164 --> 00:00:29,883
Don't be nervous.

11
00:00:30,484 --> 00:00:31,123
Ruoxi,

12
00:00:31,563 --> 00:00:32,563
I am nervous?

13
00:00:33,004 --> 00:00:34,603
It's you who's nervous.

14
00:00:35,204 --> 00:00:37,004
Look, you're sweating.

15
00:00:37,804 --> 00:00:38,483
Tell me

16
00:00:39,083 --> 00:00:40,163
what happened.

17
00:00:43,203 --> 00:00:44,163
Here you are.

18
00:00:44,483 --> 00:00:46,523
There's enough money
to last you a while.

19
00:00:46,884 --> 00:00:47,763
The password is

20
00:00:47,843 --> 00:00:49,884
the last three digits
of your birthday with mine.

21
00:00:51,523 --> 00:00:53,083
Why are you giving me money?

22
00:00:53,324 --> 00:00:54,203
I have money.

23
00:00:55,004 --> 00:00:55,884
Tell me.

24
00:00:56,284 --> 00:00:57,244
What's really going on?

25
00:00:58,083 --> 00:00:58,924
Stop asking.

26
00:00:59,564 --> 00:01:00,723
You can't help.

27
00:01:01,324 --> 00:01:02,564
I can handle it myself.

28
00:01:03,364 --> 00:01:04,083
Ruoxi,

29
00:01:04,684 --> 00:01:06,284
you're all I have.

30
00:01:06,364 --> 00:01:08,324
Don't you abandon me.

31
00:01:08,924 --> 00:01:10,724
Besides, I'm an adult now.

32
00:01:11,084 --> 00:01:12,524
If you're in trouble,

33
00:01:12,524 --> 00:01:13,363
you can tell me.

34
00:01:13,363 --> 00:01:14,964
We can solve it together.

35
00:01:16,164 --> 00:01:17,324
It's fine.

36
00:01:17,604 --> 00:01:18,524
Don't worry.

37
00:01:19,563 --> 00:01:20,563
I'll sort things out

38
00:01:21,084 --> 00:01:22,604
and explain it in a few days.

39
00:01:22,724 --> 00:01:23,524
I have things to do.

40
00:01:23,524 --> 00:01:24,604
I need to go now.

41
00:01:25,203 --> 00:01:25,923
Ruoxi.

42
00:01:26,604 --> 00:01:27,203
Ruoxi.

43
00:01:27,616 --> 00:01:30,842
=The Glory Fades=

44
00:01:30,842 --> 00:01:33,536
=Episode 24=
(Derailed)

45
00:01:41,056 --> 00:01:42,016
(ASEAN Energy Bureau Approval File)

46
00:01:42,164 --> 00:01:43,363
Energy Bureau's approval.

47
00:01:49,964 --> 00:01:52,084
We talked last week,
but they go back on their word.

48
00:01:52,643 --> 00:01:53,684
Besides He Mike,

49
00:01:53,684 --> 00:01:54,763
who else have you offended?

50
00:01:58,483 --> 00:01:59,483
Lin Shen's father,

51
00:01:59,684 --> 00:02:00,763
Director of Energy Bureau.

52
00:02:04,123 --> 00:02:06,084
There's been
too much targeting us lately.

53
00:02:06,363 --> 00:02:07,444
This is abnormal.

54
00:02:09,324 --> 00:02:10,084
Doesn't make sense.

55
00:02:10,324 --> 00:02:11,604
We put them in position.

56
00:02:11,923 --> 00:02:13,563
How did they suddenly grow so bold?

57
00:02:13,923 --> 00:02:15,404
Whoever authorized this

58
00:02:15,404 --> 00:02:16,884
must have powerful backer.

59
00:02:17,523 --> 00:02:18,592
And that backer

60
00:02:18,592 --> 00:02:20,523
must be even more influential than us.

61
00:02:21,643 --> 00:02:22,243
How powerful?

62
00:02:22,643 --> 00:02:23,363
Unlimited?

63
00:02:24,083 --> 00:02:25,284
Mr. Nie is in the Cabinet.

64
00:02:25,284 --> 00:02:26,683
If anything happened...

65
00:02:30,643 --> 00:02:32,483
Feng hasn't messaged us for a long time.

66
00:02:33,243 --> 00:02:33,803
Right?

67
00:02:47,124 --> 00:02:47,683
Go ahead.

68
00:02:49,044 --> 00:02:50,444
I've almost figured it out.

69
00:02:50,923 --> 00:02:51,844
What to say?

70
00:02:52,444 --> 00:02:53,444
There's nothing to say.

71
00:02:54,483 --> 00:02:56,324
Everyone wants a bright future.

72
00:03:00,523 --> 00:03:01,923
That's a crude lie.

73
00:03:02,363 --> 00:03:03,643
An outstanding lawyer,

74
00:03:03,763 --> 00:03:04,444
a judge,

75
00:03:04,844 --> 00:03:06,164
or a renowned psychologist

76
00:03:07,164 --> 00:03:08,923
is more honorable and respectable

77
00:03:08,923 --> 00:03:09,963
than your so-called

78
00:03:09,963 --> 00:03:10,763
bright future.

79
00:03:11,963 --> 00:03:13,363
Too many uncertainties in it.

80
00:03:13,724 --> 00:03:14,523
I can't wait.

81
00:03:15,363 --> 00:03:16,523
Becoming Madam directly

82
00:03:16,604 --> 00:03:18,483
like this is better, isn't it?

83
00:03:28,363 --> 00:03:29,164
Su Yunian,

84
00:03:29,643 --> 00:03:30,363
look at me.

85
00:03:35,363 --> 00:03:36,404
It's for her,

86
00:03:37,363 --> 00:03:38,203
(Mystery of the Beauty's Death)
your sister,

87
00:03:38,803 --> 00:03:39,488
An Ruoxi, right?

88
00:03:41,044 --> 00:03:42,004
Who told you that?

89
00:03:42,363 --> 00:03:42,963
Nonsense.

90
00:03:46,844 --> 00:03:48,064
She picked you up from school.

91
00:03:48,363 --> 00:03:49,083
I saw her,

92
00:03:49,284 --> 00:03:50,523
but never asked you about it.

93
00:03:51,164 --> 00:03:52,564
- We...
- Besides,

94
00:03:53,004 --> 00:03:54,763
you two look exactly alike.

95
00:04:02,763 --> 00:04:03,523
Don't worry.

96
00:04:04,363 --> 00:04:05,724
I'm not talking you out of it.

97
00:04:06,483 --> 00:04:07,324
I want to help you.

98
00:04:10,363 --> 00:04:11,724
I'll help you find the killer

99
00:04:12,444 --> 00:04:13,243
to avenge her.

100
00:04:42,844 --> 00:04:43,883
Ms. Bai,

101
00:04:44,363 --> 00:04:45,524
Mr. Tu and Mr. Zhao

102
00:04:45,803 --> 00:04:47,123
are so busy.

103
00:04:50,764 --> 00:04:51,524
Ms. Bai,

104
00:04:51,764 --> 00:04:52,764
Chief Zheng is also

105
00:04:52,764 --> 00:04:53,964
tied up with official duties.

106
00:04:53,964 --> 00:04:55,483
Everyone's quite busy.

107
00:04:55,964 --> 00:04:57,604
This wait isn't right, is it?

108
00:05:11,923 --> 00:05:12,764
Ms. Bai,

109
00:05:14,243 --> 00:05:15,604
I know my rank is low

110
00:05:16,003 --> 00:05:17,363
and my words carry little weight.

111
00:05:17,764 --> 00:05:19,524
It's understandable Mr. Tu and Mr. Zhao

112
00:05:20,483 --> 00:05:21,483
aren't showing up.

113
00:05:25,363 --> 00:05:26,123
Chief Zheng,

114
00:05:26,323 --> 00:05:27,363
don't put it that way.

115
00:05:28,084 --> 00:05:30,204
Mr. Tu specifically instructed me

116
00:05:30,284 --> 00:05:31,084
to make sure

117
00:05:31,084 --> 00:05:32,524
that you are well taken care of.

118
00:05:33,084 --> 00:05:33,764
Yes,

119
00:05:34,363 --> 00:05:35,883
Mr. Zhao also gave specific orders

120
00:05:36,284 --> 00:05:37,923
to take good care of you.

121
00:05:39,964 --> 00:05:41,683
This is considered

122
00:05:41,844 --> 00:05:43,323
our highest reception.

123
00:05:44,724 --> 00:05:45,644
This is called

124
00:05:45,964 --> 00:05:47,284
First Lady Diplomacy.

125
00:05:47,524 --> 00:05:48,404
Right.

126
00:05:49,644 --> 00:05:50,844
First Lady Diplomacy?

127
00:05:53,044 --> 00:05:54,443
This is...

128
00:05:56,084 --> 00:05:57,164
Let me formally introduce.

129
00:05:57,923 --> 00:05:59,644
This is Mr. Tu's partner,

130
00:05:59,724 --> 00:06:02,084
and the future madam
of Deep In The Bustle,

131
00:06:02,363 --> 00:06:03,243
Su Yunian.

132
00:06:03,964 --> 00:06:05,284
Hello, Chief Zheng.

133
00:06:05,483 --> 00:06:06,243
Hello.

134
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:09,363
Hello. I'm the Captain
of Criminal Investigation, Du Hansi.

135
00:06:09,363 --> 00:06:09,923
Hello.

136
00:06:12,844 --> 00:06:14,204
You look

137
00:06:14,323 --> 00:06:15,724
somewhat familiar.

138
00:06:15,923 --> 00:06:17,084
Have we

139
00:06:17,443 --> 00:06:18,483
met somewhere before?

140
00:06:20,164 --> 00:06:21,363
That being said,

141
00:06:21,563 --> 00:06:23,363
anyone who catches Mr. Tu's eye

142
00:06:23,524 --> 00:06:24,736
must certainly be talented.

143
00:06:24,736 --> 00:06:25,803
You'll take on

144
00:06:26,284 --> 00:06:27,483
significant responsibilities.

145
00:06:28,123 --> 00:06:29,563
Thank you.

146
00:06:29,563 --> 00:06:32,044
Just like the previous Miss An Ruoxi,

147
00:06:33,323 --> 00:06:34,604
she truly was

148
00:06:35,204 --> 00:06:38,044
a paragon of both talent, beauty,
and wisdom.

149
00:06:40,443 --> 00:06:41,524
What a pity.

150
00:06:41,883 --> 00:06:43,363
Beauty often meets an early fate.

151
00:06:50,483 --> 00:06:51,964
Miss Su

152
00:06:52,404 --> 00:06:53,964
bears a striking resemblance

153
00:06:54,284 --> 00:06:55,683
to Miss An Ruoxi.

154
00:06:56,724 --> 00:06:57,404
Yes.

155
00:07:00,164 --> 00:07:01,323
If you hadn't mentioned it,

156
00:07:01,323 --> 00:07:02,204
I'd almost forgotten.

157
00:07:02,803 --> 00:07:03,683
That case was solved

158
00:07:03,683 --> 00:07:04,563
thanks to you.

159
00:07:04,563 --> 00:07:05,803
You managed to

160
00:07:05,803 --> 00:07:06,923
get the case cleared up.

161
00:07:15,683 --> 00:07:16,284
Well,

162
00:07:17,164 --> 00:07:18,323
I have another meeting later.

163
00:07:18,644 --> 00:07:20,404
Please convey to Mr. Tu and Mr. Zhao

164
00:07:20,724 --> 00:07:21,563
we'll

165
00:07:22,003 --> 00:07:22,923
arrange another time.

166
00:07:24,563 --> 00:07:25,363
Chief Zheng,

167
00:07:26,683 --> 00:07:28,883
mind leaving your contact info?

168
00:07:33,524 --> 00:07:34,404
Sure.

169
00:07:36,672 --> 00:07:38,524
(Deep In The Bustle 888)

170
00:07:38,524 --> 00:07:39,123
Please.

171
00:07:55,084 --> 00:07:55,964
Hello, Lu.

172
00:07:57,964 --> 00:07:58,883
Zheng's left.

173
00:08:00,084 --> 00:08:01,123
Said he has a meeting.

174
00:08:01,524 --> 00:08:02,964
He seemed clearly unhappy.

175
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,512
Well, we have no choice.

176
00:08:05,084 --> 00:08:05,883
Who knows why

177
00:08:05,883 --> 00:08:07,084
they turned up suddenly.

178
00:08:08,084 --> 00:08:08,683
By the way,

179
00:08:08,883 --> 00:08:11,044
Su Yunian got Zheng's contact info.

180
00:08:19,483 --> 00:08:21,284
(What exactly was Zheng after)

181
00:08:21,284 --> 00:08:22,688
(with this sudden visit?)

182
00:08:23,764 --> 00:08:26,524
(Feng, if I'm not mistaken,)

183
00:08:26,964 --> 00:08:28,443
(this was also your doing, right?)

184
00:08:28,964 --> 00:08:30,164
(After leaving here,)

185
00:08:30,284 --> 00:08:32,243
(he probably went to report to you.)

186
00:08:35,724 --> 00:08:36,844
Come over here.

187
00:08:39,484 --> 00:08:40,404
Camera blind spot here.

188
00:08:40,404 --> 00:08:40,963
It's safe.

189
00:08:42,563 --> 00:08:43,364
How did you know?

190
00:08:44,683 --> 00:08:46,484
When they looked for you
in the parking lot,

191
00:08:46,484 --> 00:08:47,323
the camera was down

192
00:08:47,764 --> 00:08:49,843
and Ms. Bai sent me to fix the bugs,

193
00:08:50,083 --> 00:08:51,364
so I memorized these spots.

194
00:08:52,524 --> 00:08:53,443
Impressive!

195
00:08:53,644 --> 00:08:54,644
Truly the academic star.

196
00:08:55,524 --> 00:08:56,083
By the way,

197
00:08:56,484 --> 00:08:57,683
that person who came earlier

198
00:08:57,803 --> 00:08:59,232
was Chief Zheng from Police Bureau.

199
00:08:59,644 --> 00:09:01,323
He closed Ruoxi's case

200
00:09:01,323 --> 00:09:02,644
as a suicide back then.

201
00:09:03,443 --> 00:09:04,164
I think

202
00:09:04,644 --> 00:09:05,963
we might find an opening

203
00:09:06,284 --> 00:09:07,284
on him.

204
00:09:10,563 --> 00:09:11,683
Got his contact info?

205
00:09:12,284 --> 00:09:12,843
Yes.

206
00:09:13,284 --> 00:09:15,644
But I don't know
how to contact him privately.

207
00:09:17,963 --> 00:09:18,803
How about

208
00:09:19,443 --> 00:09:20,164
I give it a try?

209
00:09:20,644 --> 00:09:22,524
It might be easier if I reach out.

210
00:09:25,244 --> 00:09:25,923
Okay.

211
00:09:26,524 --> 00:09:28,203
I'll send you the phone number later.

212
00:09:28,723 --> 00:09:29,284
Alright.

213
00:09:54,963 --> 00:09:55,923
Chief Zheng,

214
00:09:56,284 --> 00:09:57,723
long time no see.

215
00:10:00,524 --> 00:10:01,484
Feng.

216
00:10:06,723 --> 00:10:08,083
Should call you Mr. Nie now.

217
00:10:09,404 --> 00:10:11,683
This is Du,
Captain of Criminal Investigation.

218
00:10:13,088 --> 00:10:13,764
Mr. Nie.

219
00:10:15,644 --> 00:10:16,603
Step out for now.

220
00:10:18,528 --> 00:10:19,244
Go.

221
00:10:29,044 --> 00:10:29,803
Zheng,

222
00:10:30,364 --> 00:10:30,764
sit.

223
00:10:31,203 --> 00:10:32,004
Sit down.

224
00:10:35,923 --> 00:10:36,843
Zheng,

225
00:10:37,723 --> 00:10:39,004
heard recently

226
00:10:39,484 --> 00:10:40,803
you've been troubled

227
00:10:40,803 --> 00:10:42,004
over my matter.

228
00:10:42,603 --> 00:10:43,524
With this cup,

229
00:10:45,244 --> 00:10:46,203
I toast you.

230
00:10:47,392 --> 00:10:48,843
I'll toast you with tea

231
00:10:49,323 --> 00:10:50,044
instead of wine.

232
00:10:55,124 --> 00:10:56,323
Fine tea.

233
00:11:02,203 --> 00:11:03,884
Last night after leaving us,

234
00:11:03,884 --> 00:11:05,963
where did Zheng say he was going?

235
00:11:07,563 --> 00:11:08,963
Had a meeting.

236
00:11:10,923 --> 00:11:12,244
But the direction he headed

237
00:11:13,563 --> 00:11:14,723
wasn't to the meeting place.

238
00:11:15,764 --> 00:11:17,404
When he first became a cop,

239
00:11:17,856 --> 00:11:18,843
who was his mentor?

240
00:11:20,884 --> 00:11:21,723
Nie Feng's father?

241
00:11:21,723 --> 00:11:23,164
He's Uncle Nie's apprentice.

242
00:11:25,884 --> 00:11:26,683
Then,

243
00:11:27,203 --> 00:11:28,764
when Uncle Nie was sick

244
00:11:28,963 --> 00:11:30,272
and we couldn't show ourselves,

245
00:11:30,963 --> 00:11:32,083
who took care of him,

246
00:11:32,524 --> 00:11:33,563
running around for him?

247
00:11:35,644 --> 00:11:36,764
You're worried

248
00:11:37,083 --> 00:11:38,884
Feng has returned without telling us

249
00:11:38,976 --> 00:11:40,764
and secretly met Zheng?

250
00:11:41,723 --> 00:11:43,203
You mean

251
00:11:43,563 --> 00:11:45,644
Tu Jiasheng could guess that we met?

252
00:11:45,884 --> 00:11:47,364
His mind

253
00:11:47,843 --> 00:11:49,963
is sharper
than your police station's polygraph.

254
00:11:53,563 --> 00:11:54,284
Mr. Nie,

255
00:11:54,884 --> 00:11:55,963
back then...

256
00:11:59,164 --> 00:12:00,644
Call me Feng.

257
00:12:03,963 --> 00:12:04,764
Feng.

258
00:12:05,443 --> 00:12:05,963
Yes.

259
00:12:06,803 --> 00:12:07,443
Feng,

260
00:12:08,044 --> 00:12:10,364
what happened between you
and Tu Jiasheng?

261
00:12:10,484 --> 00:12:11,764
The three of you were once...

262
00:12:14,683 --> 00:12:15,244
Zheng,

263
00:12:16,244 --> 00:12:18,044
the less you know about certain things,

264
00:12:18,764 --> 00:12:20,404
the better you sleep at night.

265
00:12:21,004 --> 00:12:21,764
Right?

266
00:12:26,644 --> 00:12:28,203
When the time is right,

267
00:12:29,244 --> 00:12:31,124
I'll lay all my cards

268
00:12:31,803 --> 00:12:33,404
on the table for you.

269
00:12:37,284 --> 00:12:38,284
Seems

270
00:12:39,083 --> 00:12:40,683
you're getting serious.

271
00:12:41,088 --> 00:12:42,004
He drove a police car.

272
00:12:42,004 --> 00:12:43,284
Track it now if we want.

273
00:12:44,843 --> 00:12:45,644
No need for that.

274
00:12:47,803 --> 00:12:48,644
Contact Tang.

275
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:49,920
As soon as possible.

276
00:12:51,404 --> 00:12:52,044
Okay.

277
00:12:52,164 --> 00:12:53,044
I'll contact him.

278
00:12:53,323 --> 00:12:54,164
I'll call now.

279
00:12:57,364 --> 00:12:58,164
Madam.

280
00:12:58,404 --> 00:12:59,443
Are you two...

281
00:12:59,644 --> 00:13:00,603
We're done talking.

282
00:13:00,963 --> 00:13:01,644
You two carry on.

283
00:13:01,923 --> 00:13:02,563
Okay.

284
00:13:12,524 --> 00:13:13,603
I have a request.

285
00:13:13,803 --> 00:13:15,644
Not sure if you'll agree.

286
00:13:17,244 --> 00:13:18,323
So formal?

287
00:13:21,004 --> 00:13:22,364
I want to see

288
00:13:22,484 --> 00:13:23,244
Bai Ruxue.

289
00:13:25,443 --> 00:13:26,083
Reason?

290
00:13:27,323 --> 00:13:28,923
I think she knows something

291
00:13:29,044 --> 00:13:30,364
about the day Ruoxi was murdered.

292
00:13:31,244 --> 00:13:32,203
Who told you that?

293
00:13:32,524 --> 00:13:33,723
I guessed it myself.

294
00:13:34,404 --> 00:13:35,563
Her targeting me

295
00:13:35,764 --> 00:13:37,404
proves she's not an outsider.

296
00:13:37,603 --> 00:13:38,764
She has vested interests

297
00:13:38,764 --> 00:13:39,963
in people close to you.

298
00:13:40,203 --> 00:13:41,244
That's true for me.

299
00:13:41,404 --> 00:13:42,284
And for Ruoxi,

300
00:13:42,683 --> 00:13:43,803
it might be the same.

301
00:13:47,004 --> 00:13:47,723
First,

302
00:13:48,203 --> 00:13:49,244
she might not know.

303
00:13:49,843 --> 00:13:50,404
Second,

304
00:13:50,884 --> 00:13:51,764
even if she does know,

305
00:13:51,764 --> 00:13:52,923
she might not tell you.

306
00:13:53,563 --> 00:13:54,284
Third,

307
00:13:54,644 --> 00:13:55,563
even if she tells you,

308
00:13:55,563 --> 00:13:56,803
it might not be the truth.

309
00:13:57,044 --> 00:13:57,723
Got it?

310
00:13:58,323 --> 00:13:59,083
First,

311
00:13:59,524 --> 00:14:01,524
whether she knows or not,
we need to ask.

312
00:14:01,923 --> 00:14:02,563
Second,

313
00:14:02,843 --> 00:14:03,803
I can judge whether she

314
00:14:03,803 --> 00:14:04,843
tells the truth or not.

315
00:14:05,004 --> 00:14:05,683
Okay,

316
00:14:06,164 --> 00:14:06,843
Mr. Tu?

317
00:14:14,708 --> 00:14:18,382
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

318
00:14:18,681 --> 00:14:21,872
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

319
00:14:23,704 --> 00:14:27,325
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

320
00:14:27,874 --> 00:14:30,673
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

321
00:14:32,144 --> 00:14:35,874
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

322
00:14:36,098 --> 00:14:39,595
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

323
00:14:40,994 --> 00:14:44,681
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

324
00:14:45,319 --> 00:14:50,434
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

325
00:14:51,138 --> 00:14:55,272
♪I feel guilty♪

326
00:14:55,842 --> 00:14:59,586
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

327
00:15:00,450 --> 00:15:03,893
♪Even in tears♪

328
00:15:04,642 --> 00:15:08,556
♪It doesn't matter♪

329
00:15:08,738 --> 00:15:12,561
♪We embrace in dreams♪

330
00:15:13,410 --> 00:15:16,848
♪I let down all my defenses♪

331
00:15:18,082 --> 00:15:21,445
♪Though the story has its end♪

332
00:15:22,210 --> 00:15:30,562
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
